textAfterTable: - The rent is inclusive of gas, electricity, hot water and all charges. (Heating extra off season+£100 deposit) - Please bring with you sheets and towels. - The let is from 4 pm on the Saturday of arrival until 10 am on the Saturday of departure. - Visitors are asked to leave all properties clean and tidy and particularly to clear away all left-over food. Please send your reservation with booking form and a non-returnable deposit (if dates are available) of 25% for each week to: Nira Chidgey 15 B, Quai Cdt Reveille 34300 AGDE, FRANCE Telephone / fax: + 00 33 (0)4 67 94 86 64 (Cheques made payable to Nira Chidgey) _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ Booking form Name: Address: Telephone / E-mail: Number in party: (adults): (children aged):
